Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快讓我從這裡醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳也過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃避現實
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利… 失去了亞森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:17:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:17:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們處在絕望的最底層
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 絕不能逃避現實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從嚴峻的現實中逃避是最輕鬆的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這種情況並非亞森大人所望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利埃特大人會怎麼想？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會希望妳們這麼做嗎？希望妳們選擇逃避嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會怎麼想？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會怎麼想？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個… 那個… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我這招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:54.90,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,[柯蒂利亞的顏藝是因為聞到了霸王花的腐臭味]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清醒過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人為什麼會墮落？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有池子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,墮落是為了再次爬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獅子會為了讓自己的孩子成材而把它們推下懸崖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個… 為了爬上來？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案在3秒後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案在2秒後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案在1秒後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 亨利埃特大人 亞森大人是獅子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是她的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們必須要成為
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優秀的怪盜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為優秀的偵探？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為優秀的偵探？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爬上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉睡著熾熱靈魂的小獅子們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你們的爪子撕開困難
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.43,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們的血也越過障礙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好悶熱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一如既往是個煩人的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:58.81,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,…描繪未來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已經在最底層
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不會再比現在更墮落了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 抓住這隻手爬上來吧
